      "instruction": "<p>Roll out each <strong>dough ball</strong> into a circle disc the size of a dinner plate with a <strong>rolling pin </strong>– these are your<strong> pizza bases</strong></p><p>Tip: Dust with extra sprinkles of flour as you go to stop it sticking!</p><p>Dot a quarter of your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>torn mozzarella</strong> (save the rest for later!) evenly around the edge of each pizza base</p>",
