      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and slide the <strong>stuffed crust pizza bases</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>onto the tray[s]</p><p>Add the<strong> tomato sauce </strong>onto each pizza and spread it evenly with the back of a spoon (be careful of the hot tray!)</p><p>Top them evenly with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>torn mozzarella </strong>and put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until the cheese has melted and the crust has puffed up and browned – these are your <strong>pizzas</strong></p>",
